---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms and Conditions | JILBIT"
  description="Terms and Conditions for using JILBIT.com and related ministry services."
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#000000] px-6 py-14 text-left md:py-20">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(201,146,42,0.14),transparent_55%)]"
    />
    <div class="content-shell relative">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#5cd667]">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl leading-tight text-[#faf7f2] md:text-5xl">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#faf7f2]/60">Last updated: April 18, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#f0ebe0] px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="content-shell">
      <article
        class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-8 rounded-lg border border-[rgba(92,61,46,0.15)] bg-white p-8 shadow-sm md:p-12 [&_h2]:mt-10 [&_h2]:text-xl [&_h2]:font-semibold [&_h2]:text-[#2e1a0e] [&_h2]:first:mt-0 [&_p]:leading-relaxed [&_ul]:list-disc [&_ul]:pl-6 [&_li]:text-[#7a6658]"
      >
        <p class="text-lg text-[#7a6658]">
          These Terms and Conditions (“Terms”) govern your access to and use of the website located at <strong
            class="text-[#2e1a0e]">jilbit.com</strong> (the “Site”) operated by JILBIT (“we,” “us,” or “our”). By using the Site,
          you agree to these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Use of the Site</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          You may use the Site for lawful purposes only. You agree not to misuse the Site, attempt unauthorized access, interfere
          with security or performance, or use the Site in any way that violates applicable law or infringes the rights of others.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Content and faith-based materials</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          Content on this Site is provided for spiritual encouragement, information, and ministry purposes. It is not professional
          legal, medical, or financial advice. Views expressed reflect the ministry’s religious mission unless otherwise stated.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Donations and payments</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          When you make a donation or purchase through links or forms we provide, additional terms from our payment or fulfillment
          partners may apply. You agree to provide accurate information and authorize charges you initiate.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          Text, graphics, logos, and other materials on the Site are owned by JILBIT or used with permission. You may not copy,
          modify, or distribute Site content for commercial use without our prior written consent, except as allowed by law.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Third-party links</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          The Site may link to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for their content, policies, or practices.
          Your use of third-party sites is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          The Site and its content are provided “as is” and “as available,” without warranties of any kind, express or implied, to
          the fullest extent permitted by law.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, JILBIT and its volunteers and affiliates shall not be liable for any indirect,
          incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Site.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          We may update these Terms from time to time. The “Last updated” date will change when we do. Continued use of the Site
          after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-[#7a6658]">
          Questions about these Terms may be sent to <a href="mailto:info@jilbit.com" class="text-[#2d4a3e] underline underline-offset-2"
            >info@jilbit.com</a
          >.
        </p>

        <p class="border-t border-[rgba(92,61,46,0.15)] pt-8 text-sm text-[#7a6658]/90">
          <strong class="text-[#2e1a0e]">Note:</strong> This is a general template. JILBIT should have qualified legal counsel review
          these Terms for your jurisdiction and ministry structure.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
